thread.title: Jill Tucker

author: Jill Tucker
title: Jill Tucker
text:
Company collected myself from airport within 5mins Was on my way from their office which was a couple of mins from airport. A very hot day 40 deg they had the aircon running in the car having a very comfortable start to my journey. Very friendly staff, when returning the car would they quickly drove me to the airport in plenty of time for my flight.
I would recommend Alpha Airport Rentals any time and will certainly use them again.
